snippet.title: Mizuchi (VN) Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Our friends at Aikasa Collective have a new visual novel game coming out! It is a fantasy yuri dating sim based on the Chinese story "Legend of the White Serpent". As of Aug 13 their Kickstarter campaign is live! You can check it out and back it here: http://kck.st/2OAxKSp
